<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-F5C02E3D-9B15-416D-BDB0-6A21C72A999D" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-F5C02E3D-9B15-416D-BDB0-6A21C72A999D" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title translate="no" class="- topic/title ">490053: Too many iterations needed for Waveform calibration</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-7BB038C1-38AC-40C7-A448-58EE59453F3B"><p class="- topic/p ">The temperature setting during waveform calibration is based on iteration steps. Too many iterations needed. Most likely caused by a heating problem.
</p></abstract><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-6B8D64D6-5DBB-4C07-8B4E-ABFC24BD83E1" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Collect</b> </title><p class="- topic/p "> 
<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">Patterns in calibration print</u> 
</p><table id="GUID-371361ED-DFE1-466E-95E7-A909D6525F8E" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="1.00*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="6.68*" class="- topic/colspec "/><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> C1640/C1650
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-9EDF3923-6061-499F-8F72-94DB8B99724A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-A7AF2561-119C-4924-A5CF-1832AAA6D1FE-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-A7AF2561-119C-4924-A5CF-1832AAA6D1FE-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> C1630/CMxx
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-26B8696C-8984-4551-A70B-D3A35BE9A43A" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-F91D264F-7F03-4034-9306-18B09ABA8BE0-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F91D264F-7F03-4034-9306-18B09ABA8BE0-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><p class="- topic/p "> 
<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">Calibration step</u> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This warning is generated during the calibration step "PrintheadWaveforms" which is part of one of the following calibration sequences:
</p><p class="- topic/p ">- Printhead calibration via the UI
</p><p class="- topic/p ">- SDS 04-6-026: “Execute printhead calibrations [Special Tests]”
</p></section><section id="GUID-91264740-13C2-4496-B886-2EA83E3E5280" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Analyse/Repair</b> </title><p class="- topic/p ">Restart the calibration. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">In case the warning persists escalate to LFG-CS.
</p></section><section id="GUID-9C897010-8CE8-4B5E-98EB-CFCA3D4828D9" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Evaluate/Prevention</b> </title><p class="- topic/p ">Prevent ink to expire in the engine.
</p></section><section id="GUID-7B7EB647-81DA-40F0-A214-827626DD2058" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Background info</b> </title><p class="- topic/p ">During waveform calibration, the temperature of the printheads is adjusted to set the correct ink viscosity, which is needed to get a uniform droplet size. This process is iterative. When the maximum number of iterations has been reached, this warning is generated. In most cases, this is caused by a heating problem.
</p></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-F2864082-F34C-4657-B37E-EA7C5343FE90.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Diagnostics</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
